<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 04:31:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>伊朗袭击中向以色列发射了350枚导弹和无人机；联合国召开紧急会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article-live/.premium/350-missiles-drones-launched-at-israel-in-irans-attack-un-to-convene-emergency-meeting/0000018e-dac5-d548-abef-ffffb2ae0000</link><description>以色列国防军：从伊朗发射的超过350枚导弹和无人机，大部分被拦截；以色列南部的军事基地遭受轻微损坏； 10 岁女孩受重伤 ■ 据报道，美国、英国和约旦拦截无人机 ■ 内塔尼亚胡总理与拜登总统就袭击事件进行对话 ■ 拜登：将与七国集团领导人讨论对伊朗袭击事件的统一外交反应 ■ 联合国安理会将于应以色列要求于周日</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 04:17:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article-live/.premium/350-missiles-drones-launched-at-israel-in-irans-attack-un-to-convene-emergency-meeting/0000018e-dac5-d548-abef-ffffb2ae0000</guid></item><item><title>约旦空军击落飞往以色列的伊朗无人机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/jordanian-air-force-shoots-down-iranian-drones-flying-to-israel/0000018e-da2c-d5ed-adcf-fbbe5a130000</link><description>该国北部靠近叙利亚的多个城市以及中南部地区的居民听到剧烈的空中活动</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 02:15:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/jordanian-air-force-shoots-down-iranian-drones-flying-to-israel/0000018e-da2c-d5ed-adcf-fbbe5a130000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗直接袭击以色列后，联合国秘书长对局势升级的危险“深感震惊”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/un-chief-deeply-alarmed-by-danger-of-escalation-after-iran-directly-attacks-israel/0000018e-da0b-d01b-abdf-fa7f6e1b0000</link><description>安东尼奥·古特雷斯表示，有关各方必须确保避免造成“中东多条战线上的重大军事对抗”</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 01:52:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/un-chief-deeply-alarmed-by-danger-of-escalation-after-iran-directly-attacks-israel/0000018e-da0b-d01b-abdf-fa7f6e1b0000</guid></item><item><title>200 架无人机和导弹：伊朗对以色列的首次直接攻击是如何开始的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-14/ty-article/200-drones-and-missiles-how-irans-first-direct-attack-on-israel-began/0000018e-da2f-d01b-abdf-fa7f0c860000</link><description>一名 10 岁女孩在袭击中受重伤，伊朗誓言要为 4 月 1 日叙利亚空袭造成两名将军死亡的事件报仇。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 01:49:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-14/ty-article/200-drones-and-missiles-how-irans-first-direct-attack-on-israel-began/0000018e-da2f-d01b-abdf-fa7f0c860000</guid></item><item><title>以色列要求联合国安理会就伊朗问题召开紧急会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-14/ty-article/israel-requests-emergency-un-security-council-meeting-on-iran/0000018e-da22-df04-adae-fff238070000</link><description>以色列驻联合国大使吉拉德·埃尔丹称德黑兰对以色列的无人机和导弹袭击“对全球和平与安全构成严重威胁”</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 01:39:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-14/ty-article/israel-requests-emergency-un-security-council-meeting-on-iran/0000018e-da22-df04-adae-fff238070000</guid></item><item><title>拜登返回华盛顿，誓言在伊朗发动袭击时“铁定”支持以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/biden-returns-to-washington-vows-ironclad-support-for-israel-as-iran-launches-attack/0000018e-da18-de1f-a38f-de3f9aab0000</link><description>拜登缩短周末行程，与内阁成员和其他美国高级官员会面，讨论伊朗针对以色列的导弹和无人机袭击</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 01:14:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/biden-returns-to-washington-vows-ironclad-support-for-israel-as-iran-launches-attack/0000018e-da18-de1f-a38f-de3f9aab0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗官员警告称，如果以色列对前所未有的攻击作出回应，伊朗将做出“更严厉”的反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/iranian-officials-warn-of-more-severe-response-if-israel-responds-to-attack/0000018e-d9d5-d01b-abdf-f9ff4ebb0000</link><description>伊朗国防部长警告称，任何允许以色列发动袭击的国家都将面临回应，伊朗驻联合国代表团警告美国“远离”</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 00:32:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/iranian-officials-warn-of-more-severe-response-if-israel-responds-to-attack/0000018e-d9d5-d01b-abdf-f9ff4ebb0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击以色列：发射数百枚导弹，大部分被拦截；以色列誓言回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article-live/biden-doubles-down-on-iran-warning-dont-u-s-move-additional-assets-to-region/0000018e-d491-d161-ab8f-f4f583d30000</link><description>以色列国防军：从伊朗发射的200多枚导弹、无人机，大部分被拦截；以色列南部的军事基地遭受轻微损坏； 10 岁女孩受重伤 ■ 据报道，美国、英国和约旦拦截无人机 ■ 内塔尼亚胡总理与拜登总统就袭击事件进行对话 ■ 拜登：将与七国集团领导人讨论对伊朗袭击事件的统一外交反应 ■ 联合国安理会将于应以色列要求于周日</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 23:17:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article-live/biden-doubles-down-on-iran-warning-dont-u-s-move-additional-assets-to-region/0000018e-d491-d161-ab8f-f4f583d30000</guid></item><item><title>“让我们的人民走”：数千名以色列人在特拉维夫集会要求释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/let-our-people-go-thousands-of-israelis-rally-for-hostage-release-in-tel-aviv/0000018e-d865-d5ed-adcf-fbf721260000</link><description>一名人质的女儿说，“就像逾越节一样，我们应该想象自己走出埃及……我们必须想象自己或我们 80 岁的父亲，成为加沙的俘虏。”他在加沙被囚禁的第 190 天</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 21:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/let-our-people-go-thousands-of-israelis-rally-for-hostage-release-in-tel-aviv/0000018e-d865-d5ed-adcf-fbf721260000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗对以色列的袭击将加剧各条战线的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/irans-attack-on-israel-will-fuel-the-war-on-all-fronts/0000018e-d903-de1f-a38f-df3f26b70000</link><description>拜登的警告和美军在该地区的集结可能会推迟德黑兰对周六晚间针对一名革命卫队高级人物的反应</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 20:33:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/irans-attack-on-israel-will-fuel-the-war-on-all-fronts/0000018e-d903-de1f-a38f-df3f26b70000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯表示回应加沙停火提议，要求全面停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/hamas-says-it-responded-to-gaza-truce-proposal-demands-total-cease-fire/0000018e-d8c6-df04-adae-fdd6696c0000</link><description>然而，以色列消息人士告诉《国土报》，以色列尚未收到证实哈马斯说法的信息。在伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚的儿子被杀以及与伊朗的紧张关系日益加剧之后，以色列很难决定此时是否有可能推进该协议</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 19:37:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/hamas-says-it-responded-to-gaza-truce-proposal-demands-total-cease-fire/0000018e-d8c6-df04-adae-fdd6696c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列加强紧急措施，下令关闭学校以应对伊朗袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-intensifies-emergency-measures-orders-school-shutdown-amid-iranian-threat/0000018e-d8b8-de1f-a38f-debfbd4a0000</link><description>教育部宣布“从周日开始，取消所有教育活动”，直至另行通知；全国范围内聚会人数限制在1000人以内</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 18:59:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-intensifies-emergency-measures-orders-school-shutdown-amid-iranian-threat/0000018e-d8b8-de1f-a38f-debfbd4a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列青少年被谋杀、定居者在巴勒斯坦村庄肆虐后，以色列国防军加强了西岸部队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/idf-beefs-up-west-bank-force-after-israelis-murder-settler-riots-in-palestinian-villages/0000018e-d864-de1f-a38f-de7f4a580000</link><description>据以色列军方称，数十名以色列人和巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸冲突中受伤。整个星期六，在发现一名被谋杀的 14 岁以色列人的尸体后，一群定居者进入巴勒斯坦村庄并放火焚烧房屋</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 18:17:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/idf-beefs-up-west-bank-force-after-israelis-murder-settler-riots-in-palestinian-villages/0000018e-d864-de1f-a38f-de7f4a580000</guid></item><item><title>以色列交战第 190 天：伊朗称扣押了“与以色列有关”的船只</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-190-iran-says-it-seized-ship-linked-to-israel/0000018e-d862-d01b-abdf-f87f67100000</link><description>拜登表示，他向德黑兰传达的信息是：“不要” ■ 伊朗称其扣押了“与以色列有关”的船只 ■ 以色列国防军发现失踪 14 岁以色列人尸体后，定居者在巴勒斯坦村庄发动暴行 ■ 《纽约时报》编辑委员会呼吁美国对以色列提供军事援助的条件 ■ 这是战争 190 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 17:09:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-190-iran-says-it-seized-ship-linked-to-israel/0000018e-d862-d01b-abdf-f87f67100000</guid></item><item><title>加沙谈判陷入僵局，数千人抗议政府，要求以色列各地达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-israelis-protest-government-demand-hostage-deal-across-county/0000018e-d7fb-de1f-a38f-dfff82c80000</link><description>特拉维夫、耶路撒冷、海法和贝尔谢巴正在举行示威活动。人质家属指责政府抛弃人质，呼吁驱逐内塔尼亚胡并结束战争，“如果我们必须付出代价才能让我们的亲人活着回来”</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 17:04:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-israelis-protest-government-demand-hostage-deal-across-county/0000018e-d7fb-de1f-a38f-dfff82c80000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗革命卫队在阿联酋海岸扣押一艘与以色列有关的集装箱船</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/irans-revolutionary-guard-seizes-an-israel-linked-container-ship-off-coast-of-uae/0000018e-d7ad-d01b-abdf-ffffbda90000</link><description>伊朗伊斯兰革命卫队在伊朗和阿联酋之间的霍尔木兹海峡入口处扣押了一艘与以色列 Zodiac 集团有联系的集装箱船。该船被征用并改道前往伊朗水域。伊朗没有提供任何解释，只是说这艘船隶属于以色列</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 15:05:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/irans-revolutionary-guard-seizes-an-israel-linked-container-ship-off-coast-of-uae/0000018e-d7ad-d01b-abdf-ffffbda90000</guid></item><item><title>失踪的以色列青少年确认在西岸袭击中被谋杀；巴勒斯坦人在定居者的暴行中受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/body-of-14-year-old-israeli-who-went-missing-found-netanyahu-we-will-find-the-murderers/0000018e-d737-df04-adae-fff7ff760000</link><description>一名 14 岁以色列定居者失踪几天后，他的尸体被发现。作为回应，定居者袭击了附近的巴勒斯坦村庄，袭击居民并放火焚烧财产。巴勒斯坦人报告至少八人受伤，其中一人伤势严重</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 11:41:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/body-of-14-year-old-israeli-who-went-missing-found-netanyahu-we-will-find-the-murderers/0000018e-d737-df04-adae-fff7ff760000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列监狱服刑近 40 年后，瓦利德·达卡 (Walid Daqqa) 的死亡并未让他重获自由</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-04-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/after-almost-40-years-in-israeli-prison-death-didnt-set-walid-daqqa-free/0000018e-cda3-dc93-adce-eff3d84e0000</link><description>身患重病时，没有人告诉亲人他快要死了。自战争爆发以来，他的家人一直不被允许探望他，目前尚未收到他的遗体</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 01:24:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-04-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/after-almost-40-years-in-israeli-prison-death-didnt-set-walid-daqqa-free/0000018e-cda3-dc93-adce-eff3d84e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部城镇两起枪击事件致三人死亡，警方怀疑与犯罪有关</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/three-killed-in-two-incidents-in-northern-israeli-towns-police-suspect-crime-related/0000018e-d4db-df04-adae-fddb866f0000</link><description>在 Kafr Yasif 的一次枪击事件中，一名男子被杀，四人受伤，其中包括他的婴儿和一名清真寺的伊玛目。随后，两名男子在伊斯菲亚村被杀，警方怀疑这是对先前事件的报复</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 00:50:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/three-killed-in-two-incidents-in-northern-israeli-towns-police-suspect-crime-related/0000018e-d4db-df04-adae-fddb866f0000</guid></item><item><title>所有以色列人都必须问自己：杀害 10 万加沙人是否合法？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/all-israelis-must-ask-themselves-is-it-legitimate-to-kill-100-000-gazans/0000018e-d4d2-df04-adae-fdd27f510000</link><description>为了不辜负我们 10 月 7 日所期待的同情和团结，我们必须尽一切努力制止加沙地带的恐怖</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 00:49:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/all-israelis-must-ask-themselves-is-it-legitimate-to-kill-100-000-gazans/0000018e-d4d2-df04-adae-fdd27f510000</guid></item></channel></rss>